.69 3-3.5S14.5 6 13 6z\"></path></svg></a>Al agua pato</h2>\n<p>Para terminar nos pidieron que saquemos una foto del espacio en el que ven√≠amos trabajando.\nVencido, me met√≠ a la ba√±adera sin agua y saqu√© una foto a la altura de la ba√±adera y cerr√©\nla din√°mica.</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto;  max-width: 960px;\"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/274f5b272b63abc65cbc5b4589b978d6/d932e/banadera-foto.jpg\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.833333333333336%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/jpeg;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <picture>\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/274f5b272b63abc65cbc5b4589b978d6/01472/banadera-foto.webp 240w,\n/static/274f5b272b63abc65cbc5b4589b978d6/222bd/banadera-foto.webp 480w,\n/static/274f5b272b63abc65cbc5b4589b978d6/620b9/banadera-foto.webp 960w,\n/static/274f5b272b63abc65cbc5b4589b978d6/28063/banadera-foto.webp 1440w,\n/static/274f5b272b63abc65cbc5b4589b978d6/34ef4/banadera-foto.webp 1920w,\n/static/274f5b272b63abc65cbc5b4589b978d6/050cb/banadera-foto.webp 4608w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960px) 100vw, 960px\"\n          type=\"image/webp\"\n        />\n        <source\n          srcset=\"/static/274f5b272b63abc65cbc5b4589b978d6/3bc27/banadera-foto.jpg 240w,\n/static/274f5b272b63abc65cbc5b4589b978d6/98431/banadera-foto.jpg 480w,\n/static/274f5b272b63abc65cbc5b4589b978d6/b3ee8/banadera-foto.jpg 960w,\n/static/274f5b272b63abc65cbc5b4589b978d6/b97fe/banadera-foto.jpg 1440w,\n/static/274f5b272b63abc65cbc5b4589b978d6/fb329/banadera-foto.jpg 1920w,\n/static/274f5b272b63abc65cbc5b4589b978d6/d932e/banadera-foto.jpg 4608w\"\n          sizes=\"(max-width: 960